articles.author: Greta Cross
articles.title: Graham 'Dingo' Dinkelman, known as 'South Africa's Steve Irwin', dies from snake bite - USA TODAY
articles.description: After spending a month in an induced coma caused by an anaphylactic shock from a venomous snake bite, Graham "Dingo" Dinkelman died on Saturday.
articles.content:
Conservation content creator Graham "Dingo" Dinkelman died on Saturday following a venomous snake bite he sustained in September.
